name: Violin sees violin wearing du rag on mushroom trip 003
description:
3/4 series: violin, spraypaint, acrylic pour, gold chains, photography, digital manipulation
______

Violin sees itself outside of its definition of self; ego has been questioned and is in the process of being destroyed. 
 - Based on an actual drug-free out-of-body dream that freaked me the fuck out



******
Violin represents artist, Jasminfire, who experienced a 20yr love-hate relationship with the instrument. The colors, du-rag and chains represent several identities she created around being a violinist as a defense mechanism for dealing with social anxiety and difficulty connecting with others outside of a music space.
